data.description: Great location! Call Tracy Cuffel with Razor City Realty at 307-281-0735 to view this Large 5 bed, 3.5 bath modular on a partially finished walk out basement. This property has 2 wells and is 2 lots for a total of 2.84 Acres. Tons of room in the 17X35 living room addition. Large deck on the back and front.  Large drive thru Shop. Home has easy access from highway I90. Short distance to Pine Haven, just minutes from Keyhole Reservoir.  Low utilities. Seller is currently doing some repairs and updates.
